title: DVD_Label_Cover_Art_V.2.1(Additions_Only-No_Repeats)
description:
Another Evil Bastardo Publication



Here are additional movies to add to your collection of DVD movie label cover art, includes DVD Face pics, some regular DVD case sleeves, and I&#039;ve started including the biographical write-up from the shipping sleeve. When I don&#039;t have the case sleeve I use Memorex&#039;s free label design software to create my own and I print the DVD face and the BIO on the front of the sleeve and print the title on the spine. I even use colored paper to make a colorfull collection.
